01:33:30.480 --> 01:33:35.310
What about shifting
the norms so that men

01:33:35.310 --> 01:33:37.150
who you identify as
men, and I think there

01:33:37.150 --> 01:33:38.850
are people all
across the spectrums,

01:33:38.850 --> 01:33:43.810
identifying those patterns of
behavior and changing them?

