01:37:36.195 --> 01:37:39.370
This is, we need to
change the structure.

01:37:39.370 --> 01:37:40.650
We need to change the rules.

01:37:40.650 --> 01:37:43.510
We need to change institutions.

01:37:43.510 --> 01:37:45.310
But we need to do
it in a smart way,

01:37:45.310 --> 01:37:47.400
and recognize that
the numbers of women

01:37:47.400 --> 01:37:49.320
present are going
to matter in how

01:37:49.320 --> 01:37:53.910
the rules change gender dynamics
and narrow inequalities.

01:37:53.910 --> 01:37:58.740
We need to think hard
about, is everyone present

01:37:58.740 --> 01:38:03.090
really given free and
easy access to the floor?

01:38:03.090 --> 01:38:05.730
We all need to
interrogate that, and we

01:38:05.730 --> 01:38:07.800
need to do it through
changing these rules,

01:38:07.800 --> 01:38:09.480
changing these structures.

01:38:09.480 --> 01:38:12.000
And in addition, part
of what we've identified

01:38:12.000 --> 01:38:14.310
is that a very
destructive mechanism that

01:38:14.310 --> 01:38:18.060
makes all of this work is
men's verbal aggression

01:38:18.060 --> 01:38:18.840
towards women.

01:38:18.840 --> 01:38:21.135
And so in that
sense, this is a call

01:38:21.135 --> 01:38:26.970
and an invitation to men in
general to be more self-aware.

01:38:26.970 --> 01:38:31.590
So again, this is not,
women need to change things.

01:38:31.590 --> 01:38:35.160
But rather, it is
a call for women

01:38:35.160 --> 01:38:39.450
to realize that it is
possible to gain empowerment

01:38:39.450 --> 01:38:41.040
by changing the rules.

